Subject: Unable to communicate with the server
Description: System is offline. I have reinstalled over the top and uninstalled and reinstalled the agent manually and it never comes online. We had this issue before and support were able to help. Can we do a zoom call to investigate and resolve?
Solution_Comment__c:
The customer had no available licenses for the new computers to register.
The automatic license release was enabled.
